      <title>特朗普收购案以 50,000 人的价格成交，焦点转向表现不佳的公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/trump-buyout-at-50-000-takers-as-focus-shifts-to-poor-performers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，唐纳德·特朗普总统提出的联邦雇员辞职的提议已经被 50,000 多名工作人员接受。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/trump-buyout-at-50-000-takers-as-focus-shifts-to-poor-performers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 20:08:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TSA 工作人员被告知他们不能接受马斯克的“买断”提议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/tsa-workers-were-told-they-can-t-take-musk-s-fork-in-the-road</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国联邦工作人员收到延期辞职要约两天后，运输安全管理局向其数万名员工澄清说，他们不允许参与。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/tsa-workers-were-told-they-can-t-take-musk-s-fork-in-the-road</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 20:04:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国卫生部被要求追踪“与新冠病毒相关的一切”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/us-health-agency-asked-to-go-after-anything-related-to-covid-waste</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社看到的周四发送给食品和药物管理局工作人员的一封电子邮件显示，特朗普政府正在敦促卫生与公众服务部追查“与新冠疫情相关的一切”以及“如果公开会被普通公民视为浪费”的合同。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/us-health-agency-asked-to-go-after-anything-related-to-covid-waste</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 19:41:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚公共信贷主管将于下周辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/colombia-s-public-credit-director-poised-to-step-down-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，哥伦比亚公共信贷主管在为总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗政府管理财务战略两年多后即将离职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/colombia-s-public-credit-director-poised-to-step-down-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 18:57:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将在税收法案中寻求终止附带权益并扩大 SALT</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/trump-will-seek-to-end-carried-interest-expand-salt-in-tax-bill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普在与共和党议员的会议上概述了他的税收优先事项，包括终止私募股权基金经理使用的附带权益税收减免，并扩大州和地方税收减免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/trump-will-seek-to-end-carried-interest-expand-salt-in-tax-bill</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 18:49:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法官暂时叫停特朗普和马斯克的联邦工作人员“买断”计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/judge-halts-trump-musk-federal-worker-buyout-until-feb-10</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着有关买断措施合法性的争论不断推进，一名法官暂时推迟了数百万联邦工作人员决定是否接受特朗普政府提出的辞职提议（并承诺数月全薪）的 2 月 6 日最后期限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/judge-halts-trump-musk-federal-worker-buyout-until-feb-10</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 18:24:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝森特称特朗普执政期间强势美元政策仍未改变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/bessent-says-strong-dollar-policy-remains-intact-under-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长斯科特·贝森特表示，美国在唐纳德·特朗普总统的领导下继续推行“强势美元”政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/bessent-says-strong-dollar-policy-remains-intact-under-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 18:18:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Bessent 称马斯克的 DOGE 不会改变财政体系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/bessent-says-musk-s-doge-isn-t-tinkering-with-treasury-systems</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长斯科特·贝森特 (Scott Bessent) 表示，他亲自审查了伊隆·马斯克政府效率团队中对联邦支付数据具有只读权限的财政部员工，并且表示他们没有对该部门的支付系统进行“改动”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/bessent-says-musk-s-doge-isn-t-tinkering-with-treasury-systems</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 18:13:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利会见贝莱德高管，探讨 Paschi 竞购 Mediobanca 事宜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/italy-meets-blackrock-officials-amid-paschi-s-bid-for-mediobanca</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利财政部长和贝莱德公司高管周四举行会晤，讨论了包括锡耶纳蒙特帕斯基银行 (Banca Monte dei Paschi di Siena SpA) 对 Mediobanca SpA 的收购要约在内的多个议题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/italy-meets-blackrock-officials-amid-paschi-s-bid-for-mediobanca</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 17:50:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴拿马领导人指责美国在运河争端中“撒谎”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/panama-leader-accuses-us-of-lies-in-dispute-over-canal-tolls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统何塞·劳尔·穆利诺否认他的政府已允许美国政府船只自由通过巴拿马运河，以回应唐纳德·特朗普收回水道的威胁，并指责美国“撒谎和虚假”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/panama-leader-accuses-us-of-lies-in-dispute-over-canal-tolls</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 17:22:22 GMT</pubDate>
